title: Map of Louisiana (Mississippi)

description: Map of Louisiana shows the Eastern part of the United States up to Canada; different colors are used for Louisiana (green), Eastern States (yellow), New Mexico (pink) and Canada (pink). On upper left corner, title of map embellished with an allegorical figure; below view of Niagara Falls.  In lower right corner, a vignette with the coat-of-arms of Lns.  Gall Societatis Indiae Occidentalis and below and Indian man and woman with a bull. (OPB '59)
